      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·005.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Chung fung..3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>終風且曀，不日有曀，寤言不寐，願言則嚏。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The wind blew, and the sky was cloudy;
Before a day elapses, it is cloudy again.
I awake, and cannot sleep;
I think of him, and gasp.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
