      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·005.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Chung fung..4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>曀曀其陰，虺虺其靁，寤言不寐，願言則懷。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>All cloudy is the darkness,
And the thunder keeps muttering.
I awake and cannot sleep;
I think of him, and my breast is full of pain.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
